      "text": "Tracker ([[Tracker Role]]):<br>goes around a time or two a week, asks each Programmer how she's doing, listens to the answer, takes action if things seem to be going off track. Actions include suggesting a CRC session, setting up a meeting with Customer, asking Coach or another Programmer to help. (This was discussed at [[Xp Immersion Two]] - but not much on that page.) ",
      "id": "d72e38647e3d3f51fdcada3c52625abd"
